01:45.144 --> 01:50.309
<i>In seven days,</i>
<i>God created the world.</i>

01:53.686 --> 01:55.813
<i>And in seven seconds...</i>

01:59.425 --> 02:02.019
<i>... I shattered mine.</i>

02:55.614 --> 02:59.607
- <i>I can have four new fillets overnight.</i>
- Oh, no. No, thank you.

02:59.819 --> 03:01.946
What is your name again? Ezra?
Is that right?

03:02.154 --> 03:04.884
Yes, sir. I'll just need
your first and last name...

03:05.091 --> 03:07.355
...so I can call up your account.
- <i>You know what?</i>

03:07.560 --> 03:11.462
Here's what I'm thinking, Ezra. I think
I'm gonna mail you the meat back...

03:11.664 --> 03:14.997
...so you can see firsthand the type
of dog food that you're peddling.

03:15.201 --> 03:18.693
That won't be necessary, sir.

03:18.904 --> 03:21.668
So how about we just start
with your last name?

03:21.874 --> 03:23.068
Thomas.

03:23.275 --> 03:25.140
And don't even get me started
on the pork.

03:25.344 --> 03:27.505
- Have you tried the pork?
- <i>Well, no, sir.</i>

03:27.713 --> 03:31.205
I'm not much of a meat eater myself,
but I hear really great things...

03:31.417 --> 03:32.577
...about the pork.

03:32.785 --> 03:36.016
- Oh, so you don't eat pork at all?
- No, sir.

03:36.222 --> 03:40.022
Are you Jewish?
Is that why you don't eat pork, Ezra?

03:42.194 --> 03:46.688
Well, can we...?
What's your first name, Mr. Thomas?

03:48.267 --> 03:49.734
Ben.

03:54.707 --> 03:56.038
Hold on, what was that voice?

03:56.242 --> 03:59.575
I don't... I don't have an order
for a Ben Thomas.

03:59.779 --> 04:02.179
Ezra, what was that voice?

04:02.381 --> 04:04.872
- What voice?
- Are you blind?

04:05.084 --> 04:07.609
- Excuse me?
- <i>You're kidding me.</i>

04:07.820 --> 04:13.019
A blind beef salesman
who doesn't eat meat.

04:13.626 --> 04:17.858
<i>Now, that... That is rich.</i>
<i>That is rich.</i>

04:18.063 --> 04:19.860
Have you ever had sex, Ezra?

04:21.600 --> 04:24.535
Did Lawrence in Accounting
put you up to this?

04:24.737 --> 04:28.002
Because somehow I can't imagine
the blind, vegan...

04:28.207 --> 04:30.437
<i>... beef salesman having sex.</i>

04:30.643 --> 04:33.908
- Listen, I'm trying to help you, sir.
- <i>You're trying to help me?</i>

04:34.113 --> 04:36.946
The blind beef salesman
is trying to help me?

04:37.149 --> 04:40.141
I'm actually starting to feel
pretty bad for you, Ezra.

04:40.352 --> 04:44.482
Because I look at my life, and it is
surrounded by so much beauty...

04:44.690 --> 04:47.853
<i>... and you can't see shit.</i>

04:48.060 --> 04:49.755
Is that fair?

04:49.962 --> 04:51.589
Does that seem fair to you, Ezra?

04:51.797 --> 04:54.061
Do you even know
what color the ocean is?

04:54.867 --> 04:56.494
<i>Do you?</i>

04:57.002 --> 04:59.436
- It's blue, sir.
- <i>"It's blue, sir."</i>

04:59.638 --> 05:00.900
Say what you wanna say.

05:01.106 --> 05:03.074
<i>React.</i>
<i>Say what you wanna say to me.</i>

05:03.275 --> 05:05.004
Thank you for calling
Cheyenne Meats.

05:05.211 --> 05:09.011
That's not what you wanna say,
you coward. You coward.

05:09.215 --> 05:13.242
You blind, vegan, beef-salesman,
virgin coward!

05:13.452 --> 05:16.580
- Goodbye, Mr. Thomas.
- <i>Say what you wanna say.</i>

05:37.776 --> 05:42.839
Ken Anderson. Nicole Anderson.
Allie Anderson. Ed Rice.

05:43.048 --> 05:47.485
Steven Phillips. Monica Freeman.
Sarah Jensen.

05:52.925 --> 05:57.259
Ken Anderson! Nicole Anderson!
Allie Anderson! Ed Rice!

05:57.463 --> 06:02.127
