And Sarah Jensen!

07:45.771 --> 07:47.295
Hi, can I help you?

07:47.506 --> 07:51.966
Yes. Hello, I'm looking for Emily.

07:52.177 --> 07:53.872
- You're a friend of hers?
- Yes, ma'am.

07:54.079 --> 07:55.444
- She's not home.
- Oh, goodness.

07:55.648 --> 07:58.708
No, she left this morning.
She had to do some more tests.

07:59.585 --> 08:02.213
She asked me to watch Duke
until she got back.

08:02.688 --> 08:04.383
Okay.

08:05.124 --> 08:08.025
You ever try mixing banana peel
into the soil?

08:08.227 --> 08:11.128
- Really?
- It works, I swear.

08:11.330 --> 08:15.596
Oh, would you by chance
know where I could find her?

08:23.676 --> 08:28.511
<i>Supervisor to 104.</i>
<i>Supervisor to 104.</i>

08:30.349 --> 08:31.338
Cardiac wing?

08:31.550 --> 08:33.916
Take the elevator to the fifth floor
then turn left.

08:34.119 --> 08:35.881
Thank you.

08:38.256 --> 08:42.193
Well, that's what I was just saying.
It's absolutely impossible.

08:45.698 --> 08:47.529
Hold the elevator.

08:49.368 --> 08:51.199
Thank you.

09:45.924 --> 09:47.915
Can I help you?

09:49.361 --> 09:51.352
Yes. Good evening.

09:52.397 --> 09:54.729
I'm here to see Emily Posa.

09:54.933 --> 09:58.960
