during visiting hours.

10:08.647 --> 10:10.706
Thank you very much.

11:06.071 --> 11:08.232
So if there is one thing
that I have learned...

11:08.440 --> 11:11.238
...and you all should remember
about winning these contracts:

11:11.443 --> 11:15.140
Three steps. First, tell them
what you're gonna tell them.

11:15.347 --> 11:17.315
Step two, you tell them.

11:17.516 --> 11:20.917
Step three,
tell them what you told them.

11:21.720 --> 11:23.449
We are gonna close
by reminding them...

11:23.655 --> 11:27.147
...that old girl has a 3-percent better
impulse from sea level to vacuum...

11:27.359 --> 11:31.318
...and if they pass on that, quite
frankly, they deserve another Sputnik.

11:37.002 --> 11:38.560
Now, if you will excuse me...

11:38.770 --> 11:42.331
