- Yeah, I'm fine. Look, I gotta go.

13:11.663 --> 13:14.530
Give Melanie and the kids
a hug and a kiss.

13:14.733 --> 13:17.634
I'll talk to you later.
You take care of yourself.

13:17.836 --> 13:21.932
Hold on. I know it's been a while,
but when you were staying here...

13:22.140 --> 13:26.008
