14:19.998 --> 14:23.161
Hi, my name is Ben Thomas.
I'm here to see Stewart Goodman.

14:23.368 --> 14:26.667
Inez, look at me, please.

14:27.239 --> 14:30.367
Inez. I'm speaking to you.

14:32.644 --> 14:35.772
