15:17.589 --> 15:21.958
- I'm sure that made them happy.
- Oh, hell, yeah.

15:22.160 --> 15:24.185
Now, if I could only get
my own finances...

15:24.396 --> 15:27.126
...in that kind of shape,
I wouldn't have you sitting here.

15:27.332 --> 15:28.560
No offense.

15:28.767 --> 15:30.860
That your new Beemer out front?

15:35.707 --> 15:38.733
Ben, I mean, when I found out...

15:38.944 --> 15:41.538
...that my bone-marrow transplant
wasn't successful...

15:41.746 --> 15:45.307
