impression here.

19:48.360 --> 19:50.089
I'm gonna stop by
from time to time...

19:50.295 --> 19:52.593
...make sure you're showing
these people some respect.

19:52.797 --> 19:54.992
Look, this is
a misunderstanding, okay?

19:55.200 --> 19:57.293
You don't treat people like that.

19:57.502 --> 19:59.094
Let me explain, okay, Ben?

19:59.304 --> 20:01.238
- And I'm not giving you an extension.
